WEBVTT

1
00:00:11.533 --> 00:00:14.766
Fortunately, heaven has given me a second chance.

2
00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:16.233
In this life,

3
00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:18.866
I won’t lose you again.

4
00:00:22.966 --> 00:00:24.666
Your Highness, you’re awake.

5
00:00:25.100 --> 00:00:27.033
I’ll go find the Imperial Physician right away, just a moment.

6
00:00:28.466 --> 00:00:30.033
Let me take a good look at you.

7
00:00:30.933 --> 00:00:33.233
So, the reason he’s been so kind to me lately

8
00:00:33.533 --> 00:00:35.266
is because of his guilt?

9
00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:48.633
My son, you’re finally awake.

10
00:00:48.733 --> 00:00:52.200
It’s truly the blessing of our ancestors and the protection of heaven.

11
00:00:52.866 --> 00:00:55.900
I’m fine. I’ve made Mother worry.

12
00:00:56.300 --> 00:00:58.800
Dress warmly, Wang Er.

13
00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:00.266
Rest well.

14
00:01:00.366 --> 00:01:02.966
Mother will come to see you later.

15
00:01:13.933 --> 00:01:14.766
Your Majesty.

16
00:01:16.300 --> 00:01:19.233
Have you considered what was discussed last time?

17
00:01:19.566 --> 00:01:22.533
After much thought, I still believe it’s not a good idea.

18
00:01:22.533 --> 00:01:25.366
If the Emperor finds out that I was the one who let you leave the palace,

19
00:01:25.366 --> 00:01:27.600
we will surely be at odds.

20
00:01:27.766 --> 00:01:30.300
Please do not bring this up again.

21
00:01:30.300 --> 00:01:31.100
What?

22
00:01:31.566 --> 00:01:33.800
As the Empress Dowager, you’re so inconsistent?

23
00:01:34.166 --> 00:01:34.966
Your Majesty,

24
00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:38.100
You have been taking care of the Emperor these days.

25
00:01:38.666 --> 00:01:40.433
You should return and rest.

26
00:01:46.266 --> 00:01:49.700
This is truly disrespectful behavior.

27
00:01:49.800 --> 00:01:51.066
I’m sorry.

28
00:01:51.066 --> 00:01:52.866
If I let you leave,

29
00:01:52.866 --> 00:01:54.666
the Emperor may really be in danger.

30
00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:56.733
An unstable ruler

31
00:01:56.733 --> 00:01:59.466
is harmful to the country and the empire.

32
00:01:59.533 --> 00:02:02.433
This difficult task must be handled by me alone.
